title: Measure Load Time Improvements
description: |
  Quantify the performance improvement from removing maintenance API calls:
  - Measure object screen load time before and after changes
  - Document network request count reduction
  - Measure Time to Interactive (TTI) improvement
  - Create performance comparison report

acceptance:
  - Baseline metrics documented (before removal)
  - Post-optimization metrics documented
  - Clear performance improvement shown
  - Report with before/after comparison created

